461
00:16:23,116 --> 00:16:26,184
      It's a little sweeter     
         flavor profile,        

462
00:16:26,186 --> 00:16:27,385
       and that's kind of       
        something unique,       

463
00:16:27,387 --> 00:16:29,920
          I feel like,          
       to Korean barbecue.      

464
00:16:29,922 --> 00:16:33,257
 The crust is unbelievable here.
