468
00:16:38,464 --> 00:16:39,730
       FIERI:                   
You call it a pizza oven.       

469
00:16:39,732 --> 00:16:42,266
         Me?                    
I call it wood-fired oven.      

470
00:16:42,268 --> 00:16:44,135
You've got different heats      
      going on.                 

471
00:16:44,137 --> 00:16:46,136
She won't put the pizza         
in the same spot again.         

