00:17:09,361 --> 00:17:10,695
  I could kiss you.             
            [ Laughs ]          

486
00:17:13,232 --> 00:17:15,233
     -♪ Da-da-dada, uh, mm ♪    
           -[ Laughs ]          

487
00:17:15,235 --> 00:17:16,700
      FIERI: Back in 2012,      

488
00:17:16,702 --> 00:17:19,437
    I rocked out to Ann Kim's   
        Korean-inspired,        

489
00:17:19,439 --> 00:17:22,906
        French-oven-baked       
