00:18:10,223 --> 00:18:12,956
     I know he in particular    
        hates runny eggs.       

513
00:18:12,958 --> 00:18:15,493
        Through the yolk.       
   -Don't go through the yolk!  

514
00:18:15,495 --> 00:18:16,961
      ZIMMERN:                  
This is the best part.          

515
00:18:16,963 --> 00:18:20,430
You may want to man up          
and just go for it, my friend.  

