00:18:39,585 --> 00:18:41,185
Pretty darn good, right?        

524
00:18:41,187 --> 00:18:42,453
   ...that's pretty dynamite.   

525
00:18:42,455 --> 00:18:46,323
I'm so happy right now,         
  I could kiss you.             
            [ Laughs ]          

526
00:18:46,325 --> 00:18:49,593
FIERI: But for the pizza purist,
   Ann's got an old-school pie  

