00:18:49,595 --> 00:18:52,463
       called La Creme --       
    and I do mean old-school.   

528
00:18:52,465 --> 00:18:55,065
  She's crushing those tomatoes 
         with her hands.        

529
00:18:55,067 --> 00:18:57,868
    The La Creme is actually    
    one of our simplest pies.   

530
00:18:57,870 --> 00:18:59,337
   We'll take our pizza dough,  

531
00:18:59,339 --> 00:19:02,206
      and then we'll top it     
  with the rustic tomato sauce, 

532
00:19:02,208 --> 00:19:07,345
   a little bit of olive oil,   
 salt, heavy cream, fresh basil,

533
00:19:07,347 --> 00:19:09,346
       and then it's ready      
      to go into the oven.      

534
00:19:09,348 --> 00:19:15,219
                     ♪♪         

